list.name: Changes
list.comment:
feat: Add calling reusable workflow for environment setup
Add calling reusable workflow for environment setup to the existing workflow file. This allows for the execution of a reusable workflow called "reusable_workflow_with_output.yaml". The output of this workflow is used in the subsequent step of the workflow.
